      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s been absolutely pampered and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or speck on it! It runs like an absolute dream and I've taken such good care of it. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
