    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54B32 power plant, featuring individual throttle bodies and a flawless 8,000 RPM power band. The mechanical integrity is verified by documented rod bearing service and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The exterior retains its factory luster with perfect panel gaps and zero oxidative wear. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
